data.description: Too many upgrades to mention, a must-see Taylor Morrison 1-story home completed in 2021. Located on a semi-private greenbelt lot in the Founders Ridge Dripping Springs neighborhood, this perfectly laid out "Garnet" floor plan with multiple structural upgrades including a stunning floor to ceiling rock fireplace with a hearth, gourmet kitchen and a unique elevation that is one of kind to the neighborhood. The upgraded formal dining room can be used as an additional office or movie/sitting room. Each bedroom located in a separate part of the home offering the perfect MIL,teen suite setup. There is also an amazing flex room that can be used as a reading nook, second dining space, craft area, playroom or additional office. The owners’ suite boasts a beautiful bay window with a view, a build in electric fireplace heater with a gorgeous mantel.  Primary bathroom with a large walk-in shower, separate vanities with plenty of drawers and a huge walk-in closet. Every wall in the home is insulated for improved sound barrier. Luxury vinyl plank flooring is featured throughout the home with NO carpet, custom tile in the hall bathroom and laundry room. Three (3) car garage gives you room for a golf cart or extra storage area.  The back outdoor space offers a built in Blaze Marine BBQ and an extended patio. You will not believe the sunsets over the rolling hills.  Founders Ridge community is located in the highly-rated Dripping Springs ISD school district, provides miles of walking trails and open green space, a playground, beautiful landscaping, no MUD, and low taxes (1.88%). This beautiful home is in a prime Dripping Springs location less than 1/2 a mile from Dripping Springs Elementary, Founders Park and Founders community pool, 1 mile from DT Dripping Springs, 1.5 miles from DS High School and HEB grocery store and 2 miles from DS Middle School. In addition, it has easy access to Hwy 290 with a 30 minute drive to DT Austin. Please allow one hour notice and use Showing Time.
